name: The Blue One
description:
A classic navy cushion cover with a fine grey check woven into the fabric.

Dimensions: 40cm by 40cm or 45cm by 45cm

Please note that the image and the mounting fabrics on this cushion are for display purposes. When placing an order, you are ordering the navy checked cushion cover - the mounting fabrics will differ depending on the image sent through.

Cushion inserts are sold separately, so don't forget to add one to your order if you need to!
